      </p>

      <h3>10.2 Blockchain Risks</h3>
      <p>You acknowledge that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Blockchain transactions are irreversible</li>
        <li>The Solana network may experience congestion, downtime, or forks</li>
        <li>Token values (if any economic features are activated by a community)
